>Al 56:47</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/free-freedom_liberty?lang=deu\"><small>SF</small> Frei, Freiheit</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"20\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note20a\" data-full-marker=\"20a\">\n<p data-aid=\"114227508\" id=\"note20a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/courage-courageous?lang=deu\"><small>SF</small> Mut, mutig</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note20b\" data-full-marker=\"20b\">\n<p data-aid=\"114227509\" id=\"note20b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/integrity?lang=deu\"><small>SF</small> Lauter, Lauterkeit</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"21\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note21a\" data-full-marker=\"21a\">\n<p data-aid=\"114227510\" id=\"note21a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/walk-walk-with-god?lang=deu\"><small>SF</small> Wandeln, mit Gott wandeln</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"22\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note22a\" data-full-marker=\"22a\">\n<p data-aid=\"114227511\" id=\"note22a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/56.3-5?lang=deu#p3\">Al 56:3-5</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","associated":{"p10":[{"sizes":"250px","alt":"Die zweitausend jungen Krieger","aspectRatio":"0.6896551724137931","height":"464","width":"320","missingAsset":"false","assetId":"8b2594a23909b13fd69d5ea7b6ad4398362d5c25","srcset":"https://assets.ldscdn.org/3a/66/3a66523beb762f90d1365a845f35a98f7e3bf25c/two_thousand_stripling_warriors.jpeg 60w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/ae/59/ae598110cc970adaf7c16272a534244a604091ad/two_thousand_stripling_warriors.jpeg 100w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/d9/50/d9501b9d885a5c257c415f6617f9f673dd73d11a/two_thousand_stripling_warriors.jpeg 200w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/d7/20/d